        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Chronic Condition Copay Elimination Act</strong><br> <br> This bill requires health insurers to cover, without cost sharing, preventive items and services for certain chronic conditions, such as heart disease, diabetes, and asthma.<br> </p>]]>
        </text>
